
// The code snippet demonstrates how to use the [add] slot to dynamically append nodes to a destination node's children collection. It targets the [.session] node and adds a new node containing a [role] set to "user" and a [content] node whose value is dynamically retrieved from the [prompt] argument within [.arguments].
add:x:@.session
   .
      .
         role:user
         content:x:@.arguments/*/prompt
